  "printedText": "[DON!! x1] [On Your Opponent's Attack] If you have 5 or less active DON!! cards, you may rest any number of your DON!! cards. For every DON!! card rested this way, this Leader or up to 1 of your {Straw Hat Crew} type Characters gains +2000 power during this battle.",
  "keywords": [],
  "abilities": [
    {
      "timing": "onOpponentsAttack",
